com.emc.atmos.api.request

Class ObjectRequest<T extends ObjectRequest<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emc.atmos.api.request.Request
      • com.emc.atmos.api.request.ObjectRequest<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Represents the implementation type. Allows a consistent builder interface throughout the request hierarchy. Parameterize concrete subclasses with their own type and implement me() to return "this". In abstract subclasses, return me() in builder methods.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CreateAccessTokenRequest, PutObjectRequest, ReadObjectRequest

    public abstract class ObjectRequest<T extends ObjectRequest<T>>
extends Request
    Represents an Atmos REST request dealing with a specific object.
